      <p class="- topic/p ">Direct typing option enables you to search and add products by direct typing.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To add products by direct typing, please follow the below steps:</p>
      <ol class="- topic/ol ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Go to the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Qualifications &amp; Benefits</b> page.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Enter the name of the product, which you want to add, in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product/Category </b>row in the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Product Name</b> column. Please view the below images.<fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
