                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
            <fig class="- topic/fig ">
               <image height="102"
                      placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432695/102432759.jpg"
                      class="- topic/image "/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Enter the required values to the corresponding fields for the added products.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Click <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Save.</b>
            <p class="- topic/p ">The selected products are added.</p>
         </li>
